  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK406">
<l>uḷareṉṉu māttiraiya rallāṟ payavāk </l>
<l>kaḷaraṉaiyar kallā tavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The unlearned are like worthless barren land: all that can be said of them is, that they exist.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
